WEBVTT

00:09:57.396 --> 00:10:02.135
who found those photographs
and handed them in.

00:10:02.159 --> 00:10:05.853
And he said, "You know,
I'm not the kind of guy

00:10:05.877 --> 00:10:10.079
to rat people out, but some things
just cross the line.

00:10:10.103 --> 00:10:12.175
Ignorance is bliss, they say,

00:10:12.199 --> 00:10:15.903
but you can't put
up with things like this."

00:10:15.927 --> 00:10:18.938
I talked to Steve Bolsin,
a British doctor,

00:10:18.962 --> 00:10:23.244
who fought for five years
to draw attention

00:10:23.268 --> 00:10:28.267
to a dangerous surgeon
who was killing babies.

00:10:28.291 --> 00:10:30.339
And I asked him why
he did it, and he said,